<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="14" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="5.[174,1126,744,823]" pageId="5" pageNumber="14">Etymology: We named this new species after the coloration and the horn-like humeral angles on the pronotum.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
